Cypher: MATCH (n1:Compound{ name: "Niclosamide" })-[r1:DOWNREGULATES_CdG]->(n3:Gene) WHERE NOT ((:Gene{ name: "PTPRO" })-[:INTERACTS_GiG]->(n3)) RETURN n3.name
